reviews.name: Salon Perfect Perfectly Glamorous Multi Pack Eyelashes, Demi Wispies Black, 4 pr
reviews.reviewText: I love it!! I have worn other sorts of brand of lashes for over 14 yrs and i always found them to be very uncomfortable. One day i came across these. After i bought me a pair of Salon Perfect lashes, I can truly say that these are not only worth the price, they fit so comfortably on my eyelids. they are so lightweight that i forgot i even had them on. I have got compliments of how beautiful and natural they look.
reviews.title: Natrual

reviews.name: Salon Perfect Perfectly Glamorous Multi Pack Eyelashes, Demi Wispies Black, 4 pr
reviews.reviewText: I have worn fake eyelashes for years. So rest assure, I HAVE TRIED THEM ALL. I read in a fashion magazine how comfortable these are so i tried them. I WILL NEVER BUY ANOTHER BRAND. They fit comfortably and look the most natural. The only complaint I have is that they are so popular, Walmart has an issue keeping them in stock. But so worth it!!!!!! I need to buy them in bulk! TRY THEM!!! You won't be sorry you did!
reviews.title: PERFECTION!
